      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power through its six individual throttle bodies, with the double-VANOS system operating flawlessly across the entire rev range. This chassis remains structurally pristine, featuring verified subframe integrity and factory-spec bushings. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag manual gearbox to the rear wheels through a variable M-differential lock. Finished in its original paint with a mirror-like clear coat, the exterior aerodynamics and flared arches are unblemished. Inside, the Nappa leather bolsters show zero compression, and all interior electronics function with factory precision. This is a collector-grade vehicle with a fully documented service history, ready for the most discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
